How the game will be won

Brace yourself, Honduras. The French have a powerhouse midfield with plenty of options. Didier Deschamps favours a midfield three because the players he has at his disposal are flexible, fast and fluid.

Expect them to switch positions regularly but keep the balance between attack and defence just right.

