One to watch: Paul Pogba (France)

Man Utd will be kicking themselves for letting Paul Pogba go. He was instrumental in Juventus winning Serie A and is now an all-action midfielder.

Familiar face

Hull fans will know all about Maynor Figueroa but the Honduran defender is better known for scoring a stunner from his own half for Wigan against Stoke five years ago.

